title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Nissan Navara 2010 D40 ST-X – Pre Filter Water Separator Kit Fuel Manager FM606DPK

content.rendered:
Fuel Manager Separator kit for:
Nissan Navara (2010 on) D40 3.0L
ST-X 550 V9X All models

Finally we have a vehicle specific Fuel Filter / Water Separator Kit for the Nissan Navara D40 ST-X 550 V6 Turbo Diesel. This Filter unit is to be used as a Pre Filter to separate water & contaminates thus avoiding costly repairs due to poor fuel quality. This kit includes very detailed fitting instructions and everything you will need & even where to fit it !

Kit FM606DPK Contents :
• 1x Fuel Filtration Unit Fuel Manager
Made by Stanadyne in the USA !
(Filters down to 30 Microns !)
• Mounting Bolts, washers & Nyloc nuts.
• Spare 30 Micron Filter.
• 3 Mtr of 10mm Quality Fuel hose.
• Specially Designed Filter Mounting Bracket.
• 3/8 Inch Black male Quick fit fittings.
• 4x Black 90 Degree Quick Fit Fittings
• Blanking Plugs
• Hose Clamps
• Thread Paste Sealant (6ml Tube)

Download PDF Info >

Install all fittings and plugs with the thread paste.
